OL,3,CMan fled country after conning drivers
OL,4,Cout of thousands of pounds
OL,6,FA man from Porthcawl who conned people
OL,7,Fout of hundreds of thousands of pounds
OL,8,Fthrough a car scam and then fled to
OL,9,FAmerica, has been fined by a court.
OL,11,FJonathan Riches, 46, would illegally
OL,12,Faccess the personal data of motorists
OL,13,Fand then contact them to pursue
OL,14,Fpersonal injury claims through his own
OL,15,Fcompany.
OL,17,FRiches pled guilty at Cardiff Crown
OL,18,FCourt to an offence covered by data
OL,19,Fprotection laws.
