OL,3,CMan fled country after conning drivers
OL,4,Cout of thousands of pounds
OL,6,FRiches accomplices in the crimes,
OL,7,FJamie Leong, Michelle Craddock and
OL,8,FAndrew Minty, were all previously
OL,9,Fsentenced.
OL,11,FIn court, the Judge told Riches it was
OL,12,Fa sophisticated and long-running
OL,13,Fagreement which involved a cynical
OL,14,Fbreach of trust.
OL,16,FRiches had previously been ordered to
OL,17,Fpay Enterprise Rent-A-Car a #300,000
OL,18,Fcivil settlement, then was interviewed
OL,19,Fby the criminal investigations team at
OL,20,Fthe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,21,Fthe following year.
