OL,6,FHe was first summoned to appear in
OL,7,Fcourt in 2016, which he failed to do
OL,8,Fand fled to the United States. A
OL,9,Fwarrant was then issued for his arrest
OL,10,Fand he returned and surrendered
OL,11,Fhimself to authorities in 2024.
