OL,6,FAndy Curry, Head of Investigations at
OL,7,Fthe Information Commissioner's Office,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are pleased to see justice
OL,9,Fhas been served in this case. Mr
OL,10,FRiches spearheaded a brazen operation,
OL,11,Fthrough his accomplices illegally
OL,12,Faccessing Enterprise Rent-A-Car
OL,13,Fsystems in order to steal data which
OL,14,Fhe then used to enrich himself to the
OL,15,Ftune of hundreds of thousands of
OL,16,Fpounds.
