OL,3,CMan fled country after conning drivers
OL,4,Cout of thousands of pounds
OL,6,F"His scheme, which involved the
OL,7,Funauthorised use of people's personal
OL,8,Fdata, was not only illegal, but it
OL,9,Falso meant people received nuisance
OL,10,Fcalls asking them if they wanted to
OL,11,Fmake a personal injury claim.
OL,13,F"The sentence delivered today
OL,14,Fdemonstrates justice in this case,
OL,15,Fdespite the prosecution and sentencing
OL,16,Fbeing delayed for a significant period
OL,17,Fby the defendant absconding to the
OL,18,FUSA."
